Verse 1]
I wanna fly into the sky
Break the glass ceiling if I try
I wanna fly into the sky
Break the glass ceiling if I try
My dreams are knocking out my window
And I just waiting for my time

[Verse 2]
Jaagi hoon main toh chahun main
Jo sapna tha wo sacch karun
Khud ko main dhoondhun
Khud ko main paaun
Jo mann kare wahi sunun
Meri baahon mein hai jo pari
Khilne lagi hai ab wo kali
Nanhi chiriyan meri ho gayi badi
Lage ab udi, are ab udi

[Chorus]
Kya main kahun, kaisa hoon main hairan
Zameen aur aasmaan sab hairan
Sunte hain sab armaan sab hairan
Sab dekh rahe hain udaan sab hairan hairan hairan...

[Verse 3]
Gaaye nahin kisi ne jo
Main geet naye aise gaaun
Dhoondhun nayi koi disha main
Anjani raahon pe chalun
Kehta hai mann tu hai kiran
Meri aankhon ki roshni
Tujh se hi duniya jagmagaye
Tujhse hi roshan zindagi
Chal mujhse bhi aage nikal
Ye duniya meri hi hogi kal
Jo manzile hai jo raaste
Baahein pasare mere waaste
